headline: Jinx Readies Series C Raise as It Expands Retail Footprint and C-Suite Leadership
summary: LOS ANGELES, July 16, 2025--Jinx, a leading next-generation pet food company, today announced a strategic leadership transition, significant retail expansion, and plans for a Series C funding round – all signaling a new era of accelerated growth. These developments come as the company approaches $100 million revenue milestone, solidifying its position as one of the fastest-growing brands in pet food.
